<p>Welcome to our Italian recipe website, where you'll find a variety of delicious and easy-to-follow recipes focused on two classic dishes: risotto and gnocchi. We offer simple guides to help you create flavorful meals at home, whether you're looking for a rich and creamy risotto or comforting, soft gnocchi.</p>


<h2>Risotti</h2>
<ul>
  {# Loop through the posts collection and print the titles with links #}
  {% for recipe in collections.risotto %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ recipe.url }}">
        <h3>{{ recipe.data.title }}</h3>
      </a>
    <p>{{ recipe.data.tags }}</p>
    <img src="{{ recipe.data.image }}" alt="{{ title }}" width="20%">
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul> 

